{
  "info": {
    "name": "MDSCE - API Keys",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "### Getting Started\n\n1. **Get a Firebase ID Token**: Open the MDSCE app in a browser, login as a `super` user, open DevTools Console, and run:\n   ```js\n   import('firebase/auth').then(m => { m.getIdToken(m.getAuth().currentUser).then(t => navigator.clipboard.writeText(t)) })\n   ```\n   Copy the token and paste it into the `idToken` variable.\n\n2. **Generate an API Key**: Call `generateApiKey` with a label. Copy the returned `apiKey` into the `apiKey` variable.\n\n3. **Upload a Payslip**: Use either the Raw Binary or Base64 JSON method."
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://europe-west2-mdsce-dev.cloudfunctions.net",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "idToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiKey",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "label",
      "value": "Payroll Provider",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "clientEmail",
      "value": "staff@example.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "fileName",
      "value": "payslip.pdf",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "pdfBase64",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "{{idToken}}",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "generateApiKey",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.result?.apiKey) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('apiKey', json.result.apiKey);",
                  "  console.log('API Key saved to variable:', json.result.apiKey);",
                  "}",
                  ""
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"label\": \"{{label}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/generateApiKey",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["generateApiKey"]
            },
            "description": "Generates a new API key. If a key with the same label already exists, it is replaced.\n\n**Auth:** Set via the Admin folder's Authorization tab (Bearer token using `{{idToken}}`)\n\n**Test script** auto-saves the returned `apiKey` into the `apiKey` collection variable."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "revokeApiKey",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"label\": \"{{label}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/revokeApiKey",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["revokeApiKey"]
            },
            "description": "Revokes an API key by deleting its Firestore document.\n\n**Auth:** Set via the Admin folder's Authorization tab (Bearer token using `{{idToken}}`)."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Admin endpoints requiring Firebase Auth (super role)."
    },
    {
      "name": "Public",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload via file upload",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-API-Key",
                "value": "{{apiKey}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "file",
              "file": {
                "src": "/Users/joseph/worktrees/mdsce/send-staff-email/data/payslip.pdf"
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/uploadPayslipExternal?clientEmail={{clientEmail}}&fileName={{fileName}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["uploadPayslipExternal"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "clientEmail",
                  "value": "{{clientEmail}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "fileName",
                  "value": "{{fileName}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Uploads a payslip by selecting a PDF file directly.\n\n**Auth:** `X-API-Key` header (no Firebase Auth needed)\n\n**Body:** Use the binary file picker to select your PDF.\n\n**Query params:** `clientEmail` (required) and `fileName` (optional, defaults to payslip.pdf)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upload via base64",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-API-Key",
                "value": "{{apiKey}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fileBase64\": \"{{pdfBase64}}\",\n  \"fileName\": \"{{fileName}}\",\n  \"clientEmail\": \"{{clientEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/uploadPayslipExternal",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["uploadPayslipExternal"]
            },
            "description": "Uploads a payslip using base64-encoded text.\n\n**Auth:** `X-API-Key` header (no Firebase Auth needed)\n\n**Generate pdfBase64 before sending:**\n```bash\nbase64 -i /path/to/payslip.pdf | pbcopy\n```\nThen paste the value into the `pdfBase64` collection variable."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Public endpoints requiring only an API Key."
    }
  ]
}
